#. <section class="sutta" id="sn42.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn42.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 42"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 42"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn42.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Gāmaṇivagga"
msgstr "1. Chiefs"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn42.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Maṇicūḷakasutta"
msgstr "10. With Maṇicūḷaka"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.10:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the "
"squirrels’ feeding ground."

msgctxt "sn42.10:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena rājantepure rājaparisāya sannisinnānaṃ sannipatitānaṃ "
"ayamantarākathā udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"Now at that time while the king’s retinue was sitting together in the royal "
"compound this discussion came up among them:"

msgctxt "sn42.10:1.3"
msgid ""
"“kappati samaṇānaṃ sakyaputtiyānaṃ jātarūparajataṃ, sādiyanti samaṇā "
"sakyaputtiyā jātarūparajataṃ, paṭiggaṇhanti samaṇā sakyaputtiyā "
"jātarūparajatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Gold and money are proper for Sakyan ascetics. They accept and receive gold "
"and money.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.326"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.10:2.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena maṇicūḷako gāmaṇi tassaṃ parisāyaṃ nisinno hoti."
msgstr "Now at that time the chief Maṇicūḷaka was sitting in that assembly."

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.2"
msgid "Atha kho maṇicūḷako gāmaṇi taṃ parisaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "He said to that retinue:"

#. VAR: ayyo → ayyā (bj, s3, pts1)
msgctxt "sn42.10:2.3"
msgid "“mā ayyo evaṃ avacuttha."
msgstr "“Good sirs, don’t say that."

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.4"
msgid ""
"Na kappati samaṇānaṃ sakyaputtiyānaṃ jātarūparajataṃ, na sādiyanti samaṇā "
"sakyaputtiyā jātarūparajataṃ, nappaṭiggaṇhanti samaṇā sakyaputtiyā "
"jātarūparajataṃ, nikkhittamaṇisuvaṇṇā samaṇā sakyaputtiyā "
"apetajātarūparajatā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Gold and money are not proper for Sakyan ascetics. They neither accept nor "
"receive gold and money. They have set aside gems and gold, and rejected gold "
"and money.”"

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.5"
msgid "Asakkhi kho maṇicūḷako gāmaṇi taṃ parisaṃ saññāpetuṃ."
msgstr "He was able to persuade that assembly."

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.6"
msgid ""
"Atha kho maṇicūḷako gāmaṇi yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho maṇicūḷako "
"gāmaṇi bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Maṇicūḷaka went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told "
"him what had happened. He then said:"

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.7"
msgid ""
"“idha, bhante, rājantepure rājaparisāya sannisinnānaṃ sannipatitānaṃ "
"ayamantarākathā udapādi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.8"
msgid ""
"‘kappati samaṇānaṃ sakyaputtiyānaṃ jātarūparajataṃ, sādiyanti samaṇā "
"sakyaputtiyā jātarūparajataṃ, paṭiggaṇhanti samaṇā sakyaputtiyā "
"jātarūparajatan’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.9"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, bhante, taṃ parisaṃ etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.10"
msgid "‘mā ayyo evaṃ avacuttha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.11"
msgid ""
"Na kappati samaṇānaṃ sakyaputtiyānaṃ jātarūparajataṃ, na sādiyanti samaṇā "
"sakyaputtiyā jātarūparajataṃ, nappaṭiggaṇhanti samaṇā sakyaputtiyā "
"jātarūparajataṃ, nikkhittamaṇisuvaṇṇā samaṇā sakyaputtiyā "
"apetajātarūparajatā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.12"
msgid "Asakkhiṃ khvāhaṃ, bhante, taṃ parisaṃ saññāpetuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.10:2.13"
msgid ""
"Kaccāhaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākaramāno vuttavādī ceva bhagavato homi, na ca "
"bhagavantaṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhāmi, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ byākaromi, na ca "
"koci sahadhammiko vādānuvādo gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Answering this way, I trust that I repeat what the Buddha has said, and don’"
"t misrepresent him with an untruth. I trust my explanation is in line with "
"the teaching, and that there are no legitimate grounds for rebuke or "
"criticism.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.327"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.10:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Taggha tvaṃ, gāmaṇi, evaṃ byākaramāno vuttavādī ceva me hosi, na ca maṃ "
"abhūtena abbhācikkhasi, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ byākarosi, na ca koci "
"sahadhammiko vādānuvādo gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchati."
msgstr ""
"“Indeed, in answering this way you repeat what I’ve said, and don’t "
"misrepresent me with an untruth. Your explanation is in line with the "
"teaching, and there are no legitimate grounds for rebuke or criticism."

msgctxt "sn42.10:3.2"
msgid ""
"Na hi, gāmaṇi, kappati samaṇānaṃ sakyaputtiyānaṃ jātarūparajataṃ, na "
"sādiyanti samaṇā sakyaputtiyā jātarūparajataṃ, nappaṭiggaṇhanti samaṇā "
"sakyaputtiyā jātarūparajataṃ, nikkhittamaṇisuvaṇṇā samaṇā sakyaputtiyā "
"apetajātarūparajatā."
msgstr ""
"Gold and money are not proper for Sakyan ascetics. They neither accept nor "
"receive gold and money. They have set aside gems and gold, and rejected gold "
"and money."

# Here again I don’t see how we can say “allowable”.
msgctxt "sn42.10:3.3"
msgid ""
"Yassa kho, gāmaṇi, jātarūparajataṃ kappati, pañcapi tassa kāmaguṇā kappanti."
msgstr ""
"If gold and silver were proper for them, then the five kinds of sensual "
"stimulation would also be proper."

#. VAR: () → (tassapi jātarūparajataṃ kappati) (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn42.10:3.4"
msgid ""
"Yassa pañca kāmaguṇā kappanti (), ekaṃsenetaṃ, gāmaṇi, dhāreyyāsi "
"assamaṇadhammo asakyaputtiyadhammoti."
msgstr ""
"And if the five kinds of sensual stimulation are proper for them, you should "
"definitely regard them as not having the qualities of an ascetic or a "
"follower of the Sakyan."

msgctxt "sn42.10:3.5"
msgid "Api cāhaṃ, gāmaṇi, evaṃ vadāmi—"
msgstr "Rather, chief, I say this:"

#. VAR: pariyesitabboti
msgctxt "sn42.10:3.6"
msgid ""
"tiṇaṃ tiṇatthikena pariyesitabbaṃ, dāru dārutthikena pariyesitabbaṃ, sakaṭaṃ "
"sakaṭatthikena pariyesitabbaṃ, puriso purisatthikena pariyesitabbo."
msgstr ""
"Straw may be looked for by one needing straw; wood may be looked for by one "
"needing wood; a cart may be looked for by one needing a cart; a workman may "
"be looked for by one needing a workman."

msgctxt "sn42.10:3.7"
msgid ""
"Na tvevāhaṃ, gāmaṇi, kenaci pariyāyena ‘jātarūparajataṃ sāditabbaṃ "
"pariyesitabban’ti vadāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"But I say that there is no way they can accept or look for gold and money.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn42.10:3.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
